THE GAME
--------

  'NixNext' is a Workbench game where you click on tiles, which
causes neighbouring tiles to 'blow-up'. If neighbouring tiles are
of the same type as the clicked tile, these tiles will be
eliminated and will be replaced by new tiles, otherwise, they will
reappear. However, the clicked tile will stay in place...

  The game starts with 3 types of tiles and as the game
progresses, other types of tiles are added from time to time...

  The game ends when there are no tiles of the same type next to
each other...

  Have fun!

